The Director-General of the National Intelligence Coordinating Agency, the

Chief of Staff of the Armed Forces of the Philippines, the Chief of the Philippine
National Police, and the Director of the National Bureau of Investigation shall attend
the meetings of the Council as may be necessary to advise and assist in its
deliberations. The Governor of the Bangko Sentral ng Pilipinas may also be invited to
participate in the NSC.

Section 2. Reorganization of the Executive Committee of NSC. The

Executive Committee of the NSC is hereby reorganized and shall now be composed
